_sText:
tv-tower_s_beta by HappyManVan

---------------------------------------

This is a remake of tv-tower from Counter-Strike 1.6. 

This is only a beta and is definantly not fine tuned for a full release. 

This is also my first ever map.

Known issues:
-After elevator comes back down, it isn't flush with ground.
-Glass upstairs is too clear.

How to install:

Place tv-tower_s_beta.bsp and tv-tower_s_beta.nav into C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\*steamaccount*\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Thanks to ED Bickel for helping me out with my first map.

Thanks for playing this map, if you know how to fix any known issues (so I don't have to waste time figuring out how to) or see an issue/suggestion, email me at element32d@yahoo.com
